        "## 📖 Part 1: Multi-Head Attention\n",
        "\n",
        "**Multi-Head Attention** is the core innovation of transformers. It allows the model to focus on different parts of the input simultaneously.\n",
        "\n",
        "### How It Works:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Query (Q), Key (K), Value (V):** Linear projections of input\n",
        "2. **Attention Scores:** Compute similarity between Q and K\n",
        "3. **Weighted Values:** Apply scores to V\n",
        "4. **Multiple Heads:** Repeat process with different projections\n",
        "\n",
        "### Formula:\n",
        "```\n",
        "Attention(Q, K, V) = softmax(QK^T / √d_k) V\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
      ]
    }
  ],
